en_723853_0	Troops of the Security Force Headquarters - Central (SFHQ-Cen) on Tuesday (1) for the benefit of patients in Diyatalawa area donated their blood during a blood collection arrangement, organized and held at Diyatalawa Maha Vidyalaya premises by teachers and students.
en_723853_1	A group of 31 Army troops gave blood during this campaign where school teachers and students joined together.
en_723853_2	The Civil Coordination Officer and the troops under the guidance of Major General Laksiri Waduge, Commander, Security Forces - Central took part in the programme.
en_723853_3	Diyatalawa Maha Vidyalaya had turned to the SFHQ-Cen for assistance in this regard.
